                        <interp inst="t18380226-name-823" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES EATON</persName>
                  </hi>. I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former convic<lb></lb>tion, from Mr. Clark's office-(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the person who was tried and convicted.</p>
